column5: Bet this guy has no problems casting around docks
Kewl..  i KNEW i could use my fishing equipmen to keep my inlaws at bay somehow ! lol
I called this a casting machine    Docks won't be a problem for him for sure  I bet ya if he got snagged on your dock and a nail came loose..... He'd drive that nail back without you noticing!!  LM
Yeah but he can catch fish..... LOL
